This test will check that Gnome Calculator can be opened either from a terminal window or from the applications menu, and shutdown
<dl>
    <dt>Open a terminal window, type <code>gnome-calculator</code> at the prompt and hit the "Enter" key</dt>
        <dd>Calculator opens</dd>
    <dt>Click the top right "X" of the window's title bar to close the application</dt>
        <dd>Calculator closes</dd>
    <dt>Point your mouse pointer to the Applications Menu icon and click it</dt>
        <dd>A menu drops down</dd>
    <dt>Navigate to Accessories -> Calculator</dt>
        <dd>Calculator opens</dd>
</dl>

This test will check that Gnome Calculator's Application menu options work as expected
